text: i tried many deep fried foods, this shop is the most of the best in SG

Very normal curry puff. Not spicy and the crust is thick.

I prefer thin crust with spicy filling.
Have not try the rest. But you tiao is 5 stars.  Not oily and nice salty flavour that goes so well with coffee.

Just tried the "Butterfly", dipped in coffee. Nice and hot and huge. Everything in this store is priced at $1, including the curry puff. Will try that in my next visit. Redhill food centre is a gem.

Tried the mini Youtiao - even though not hot, soft and light. Love it! Got another $2 (3 for $1).

Overall:
Youtiao - 5 stars
Mini Youtiao - 4 stars (inconsistent- was not cooked properly the 2nd time I got this.)
Butterfly - 5 stars
Tapioca - 4 stars
Curry Puff - don't like this.

Accepts CDC vouchers.
I like carrot cake, and this stall delivers.
